comment:
* Class to hold input to measurement registration calls.
 * @hide

variables.name: INVALID
variables.comment: Invalid registration type used as a default.

variables.name: REGISTER_SOURCE
variables.comment:
* A request to register an Attribution Source event (NOTE: AdServices type not
     * android.context.AttributionSource).

variables.name: REGISTER_TRIGGER
variables.comment: A request to register a trigger event.

methods.name: public int describeContents()
methods.comment: * For Parcelable, no special marshalled objects.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel out, int flags)
methods.comment: * For Parcelable, write out to a Parcel in particular order.

methods.name: public Uri getRegistrationUri()
methods.comment: Source URI of the App / Publisher.

methods.name: public InputEvent getInputEvent()
methods.comment: InputEvent related to an ad event.

methods.name: public String getAppPackageName()
methods.comment: Package name of the app used for the registration.

methods.name: public String getSdkPackageName()
methods.comment: Package name of the sdk used for the registration.

methods.name: public long getRequestTime()
methods.comment: Time the request was created, as millis since boot excluding time in deep sleep.

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel out, int flags)
